{"tid":2052861,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【前妻暗示六年冇夫妻性生活】冷對張利華為婚外情認錯 魏駿傑心死：再唔走真係太遲","createTime":"2020-06-05T21:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T03:35:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b85ac100595607cc2512f751780a09664a994ee7","tid":2052861,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T21:38:28.000Z","msg":"52歲魏駿傑與32歲重慶嫩妻張利華離婚收場，是很多老夫少妻中港婚姻的寫照。<br />\n<br />\n對於張利華向本刊暗示，六年來沒夫妻性生活，更以「情感缺失」形容自己在這段婚姻中有多寂寞難耐，甚至她為婚外情公開認錯，魏駿傑一點也不為所動，早已心死的他，只冷冷拋下一句：「再唔走就真係太遲！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_743819_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_743819_0&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=bcdb6d09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_743819_0&h=54e1bba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_743819_0</a>"},{"pid":"e7a85bb4c3276bed73a44d0314b82607a8a19978","tid":2052861,"uid":121721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T21:46:47.000Z","msg":"識時務者"},{"pid":"b2af4427251e5f2f14d50c6d01ac5603dd3c817a","tid":2052861,"uid":229397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7a85bb4c3276bed73a44d0314b82607a8a19978","tid":2052861,"uid":121721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T21:46:47.000Z","msg":"識時務者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T21:57:55.000Z","msg":"張利華"},{"pid":"ee0c2729580516d0c6c56229adb37fd412772496","tid":2052861,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7a85bb4c3276bed73a44d0314b82607a8a19978","tid":2052861,"uid":121721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T21:46:47.000Z","msg":"識時務者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"佢係不識時務者"}]}